WEBVTT

00:00:01.692 --> 00:00:05.937
Há duas semanas, pesquisei
a palavra "nacionalista" no Twitter.

00:00:06.109 --> 00:00:08.060
Os resultados foram bastante diversos,

00:00:08.104 --> 00:00:11.327
com expressões como, 
"Parvo Racista Encorajado,"

00:00:11.351 --> 00:00:12.361
(Risos)

00:00:12.385 --> 00:00:14.300
"Idiota Suprematista Branco,"

00:00:14.534 --> 00:00:16.360
"Fantoches fascistas,"

00:00:16.504 --> 00:00:17.512
(Risos)

00:00:17.626 --> 00:00:20.349
"Orwelliano, Hitleriano, Aterrador."

00:00:20.373 --> 00:00:22.540
Depois pesquisei a palavra "globalista"

00:00:22.564 --> 00:00:25.496
e obtive resultados como, 
"Socialistas Interesseiros,"

00:00:25.790 --> 00:00:28.420
"Repugnante Propaganda Corporativa,"

00:00:28.774 --> 00:00:31.389
"Soberanos Financeiros Elitistas",